---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';
---

<Layout title="Men's Coaching Blog - Tom Jameson">
    <div class="blog-container">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="blog-header">
                <h1>Men's Coaching Blog</h1>
                <p>Insights, strategies, and guidance for men navigating life's challenges and opportunities.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="blog-grid">
                <article class="blog-card">
                    <div class="blog-meta">
                        <span class="category">Career Coaching</span>
                        <span class="date">December 2024</span>
                    </div>
                    <h2><a href="/blog/mens-coach-santa-monica">Best Men's Coaching in Santa Monica</a></h2>
                    <p>Discover why Santa Monica is home to some of the most effective men's coaching services, and how professional guidance can transform your career and personal life.</p>
                    <a href="/blog/mens-coach-santa-monica" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
                </article>

                <article class="blog-card">
                    <div class="blog-meta">
                        <span class="category">Career Development</span>
                        <span class="date">December 2024</span>
                    </div>
                    <h2><a href="/blog/mens-career-coaching">Men's Career Coaching: Breaking Through Professional Barriers</a></h2>
                    <p>Learn how men's career coaching can help you overcome workplace challenges, advance your career, and achieve professional fulfillment.</p>
                    <a href="/blog/mens-career-coaching" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
                </article>

                <article class="blog-card">
                    <div class="blog-meta">
                        <span class="category">Personal Growth</span>
                        <span class="date">December 2024</span>
                    </div>
                    <h2><a href="/blog/mens-life-coach-anxiety">Men's Life Coach for Anxiety and Depression</a></h2>
                    <p>How professional men's life coaching provides effective support for anxiety and depression, offering practical strategies for mental wellness.</p>
                    <a href="/blog/mens-life-coach-anxiety" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
                </article>

                <article class="blog-card">
                    <div class="blog-meta">
                        <span class="category">Relationships</span>
                        <span class="date">December 2024</span>
                    </div>
                    <h2><a href="/blog/mens-coaching-divorce">Men's Coaching Through Divorce: Rebuilding Your Life</a></h2>
                    <p>Navigate the challenges of divorce with professional men's coaching support, learning to rebuild confidence and create a new path forward.</p>
                    <a href="/blog/mens-coaching-divorce" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
                </article>

                <article class="blog-card">
                    <div class="blog-meta">
                        <span class="category">Family</span>
                        <span class="date">December 2024</span>
                    </div>
                    <h2><a href="/blog/mens-family-coaching">Men's Family Coaching: Strengthening Fatherhood and Relationships</a></h2>
                    <p>Discover how men's family coaching can help you become a better father, partner, and family leader while maintaining your personal growth.</p>
                    <a href="/blog/mens-family-coaching" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
                </article>

                <article class="blog-card">
                    <div class="blog-meta">
                        <span class="category">Leadership</span>
                        <span class="date">December 2024</span>
                    </div>
                    <h2><a href="/blog/mens-leadership-coaching">Men's Leadership Coaching: Developing Executive Presence</a></h2>
                    <p>Build executive presence and leadership skills through targeted men's coaching that focuses on communication, decision-making, and team management.</p>
                    <a href="/blog/mens-leadership-coaching" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
                </article>

                <article class="blog-card">
                    <div class="blog-meta">
                        <span class="category">Midlife</span>
                        <span class="date">December 2024</span>
                    </div>
                    <h2><a href="/blog/mens-midlife-coaching">Men's Midlife Coaching: Navigating Life Transitions</a></h2>
                    <p>Navigate midlife transitions with confidence through professional men's coaching that addresses career changes, relationship shifts, and personal fulfillment.</p>
                    <a href="/blog/mens-midlife-coaching" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
                </article>

                <article class="blog-card">
                    <div class="blog-meta">
                        <span class="category">Personal Development</span>
                        <span class="date">December 2024</span>
                    </div>
                    <h2><a href="/blog/mens-personal-coaching">Men's Personal Coaching: Building Confidence and Self-Worth</a></h2>
                    <p>Transform your self-confidence and personal worth through targeted men's coaching that addresses limiting beliefs and builds authentic strength.</p>
                    <a href="/blog/mens-personal-coaching" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
                </article>
            </div>

            <div class="blog-cta">
                <h3>Ready to Start Your Transformation?</h3>
                <p>Take the first step towards achieving your goals with professional men's coaching.</p>
                <a href="/#contact" class="btn">Book Your Consultation Today</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <style>
        .blog-container {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: white;
            padding: 80px 0;
        }

        .blog-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }

        .blog-header h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #172a22;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .blog-header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #666;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .blog-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }

        .blog-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }

        .blog-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .blog-meta {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .category {
            background: #d0c39b;
            color: #172a22;
            padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        .date {
            color: #666;
        }

        .blog-card h2 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #172a22;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .blog-card h2 a {
            color: inherit;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .blog-card h2 a:hover {
            color: #d0c39b;
        }

        .blog-card p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .read-more {
            color: #d0c39b;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .read-more:hover {
            color: #172a22;
        }

        .blog-cta {
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #172a22 0%, #1e3a2e 100%);
            color: #d0c39b;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .blog-cta h3 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .blog-cta p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #d0c39b;
            color: #172a22;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(208, 195, 155, 0.3);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #c4b082;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(208, 195, 155, 0.4);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .blog-header h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            
            .blog-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .blog-card {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</Layout>
